---
import AnimatedButton from "@/components/AnimatedButton.astro";
import SectionHeading from "@/components/SectionHeading.astro";
---

<section class="commerce-ready-section">
  <div class="container">
    <SectionHeading
      eyebrow="Future Commerce"
      title="为电子书、音频合集和会员内容预留商业位置"
      text="不是先堆功能，而是先把未来会变现的内容形态用品牌级版面摆出来。"
      align="center"
    />
    <div class="commerce-panels">
      <article class="commerce-panel commerce-panel-a reveal">
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>睡前历史音频合集</h3>
        <p>把长篇历史内容整理成系列音频，适合未来做付费合集或会员内容。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="commerce-panel commerce-panel-b reveal">
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>主题电子书</h3>
        <p>把朝代、人物、城市专题整理成可下载电子书，形成稳定内容资产。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="commerce-panel commerce-panel-c reveal">
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>品牌周边与课程</h3>
        <p>从内容站自然延展到知识产品、收藏卡、课程和合作广告位。</p>
      </article>
    </div>
    <div class="commerce-action reveal">
      <AnimatedButton href="/contact/" label="洽谈合作" variant="ghost" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
